column5: Thanks Pete, that was hilarious and at least a couple names came to mind
Thanks Pete! Reminds me of a certain young lad.. heck even kinda looks like him!
I know its not fishing, but enough of us probably play in the "Beer Leagues" and this reminded me of it, a bit older but...  Life in the Beer Leagues
Yeah a few came to mind for me also,too funny for sure.
